<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Executive IT — Flux & Intégration</title>
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;700&family=Playfair+Display:wght@700&display=swap');

    :root {
      --navy: #0a192f;
      --gold: #c5a059;
      --slate: #64748b;
      --bg: #f8fafc;
      --white: #ffffff;
      --border: #e2e8f0;
      --teal: #2dd4bf;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background: var(--bg); color: var(--navy); display: flex; }

    /* Sidebar Corporate */
    .sidebar { width: 280px; height: 100vh; background: var(--navy); color: white; position: sticky; top: 0; padding: 40px 0; }
    .logo { padding: 0 30px 30px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); }
    .logo h1 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 22px; }
    .logo span { color: var(--gold); font-size: 10px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px; display: block; }

    .nav-item { padding: 15px 30px; font-size: 13px; cursor: pointer; color: #cbd5e1; transition: 0.3s; border-left: 3px solid transparent; }
    .nav-item.active { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); color: white; border-left-color: var(--gold); font-weight: 600; }

    /* Main */
    .main { flex: 1; padding: 60px; max-width: 1300px; }
    .header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-end; margin-bottom: 40px; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--navy); padding-bottom: 20px; }
    .header h2 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 32px; }

    /* Flux Layout */
    .panel { background: var(--white); border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 30px; margin-bottom: 30px; }
    .panel-title { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 25px; border-left: 3px solid var(--gold); padding-left: 15px; }

    .flux-container { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.5fr; gap: 30px; }

    /* Circle Map Visual Mock */
    .circle-viz { width: 220px; height: 220px; border-radius: 50%; border: 8px double var(--border); margin: 0 auto; position: relative; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
    .circle-viz::after { content: "HUB"; font-weight: 800; color: var(--gold); font-size: 12px; }
    .node-dot { position: absolute; width: 8px; height: 8px; background: var(--navy); border-radius: 50%; }

    /* Flow Table */
    .flow-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 15px; }
    .flow-card { padding: 15px; background: #f8fafc; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-left: 3px solid var(--navy); }
    .flow-card strong { font-size: 13px; display: block; margin-bottom: 5px; }
    .flow-card span { font-size: 11px; color: var(--slate); text-transform: uppercase; }

    /* Stats */
    .stat-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 12px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); font-size: 13px; }
    .stat-val { font-weight: 700; color: var(--navy); }

  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <nav class="sidebar">
    <div class="logo">
      <h1>Executive IT</h1>
      <span>Architecture & Gouvernance</span>
    </div>
    <div class="nav-item">Vue Stratégique</div>
    <div class="nav-item">Portefeuille Apps</div>
    <div class="nav-item">TRM — Risques</div>
    <div class="nav-item">Finance IT</div>
    <div class="nav-item">Conformité & Data</div>
    <div class="nav-item active">Flux & Intégration</div>
    <div class="nav-item">Sourcing & Vendors</div>
  </nav>

  <main class="main">
    <header class="header">
      <h2>Intégration & Flux</h2>
      <div style="font-size: 12px; color: var(--slate);">CARTOGRAPHIE DES ÉCHANGES</div>
    </header>

    <div class="flux-container">
      <div class="panel">
        <div class="panel-title">Densité des Interfaces</div>
        <div class="circle-viz">
           <div class="node-dot" style="top: 10%; left: 50%;"></div>
           <div class="node-dot" style="top: 85%; left: 30%;"></div>
           <div class="node-dot" style="top: 40%; right: 5%;"></div>
           <div class="node-dot" style="bottom: 20%; right: 15%;"></div>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-top: 30px;">
          <div class="stat-row"><span>Total Interfaces</span><span class="stat-val">142</span></div>
          <div class="stat-row"><span>Flux Critiques (Temps Réel)</span><span class="stat-val">34</span></div>
          <div class="stat-row"><span>Taux de Redondance</span><span class="stat-val">12%</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="panel">
        <div class="panel-title">Principaux Hubs d'Échange</div>
        <div class="flow-grid">
          <div class="flow-card">
            <span>Core System</span>
            <strong>ERP Central</strong>
            <p style="font-size: 11px; color: var(--slate); margin-top: 5px;">Concentrateur de flux financier et logistique.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flow-card">
            <span>Customer Hub</span>
            <strong>CRM & Front-End</strong>
            <p style="font-size: 11px; color: var(--slate); margin-top: 5px;">Synchronisation des données clients omnicanales.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flow-card">
            <span>Analytics Hub</span>
            <strong>Data Platform</strong>
            <p style="font-size: 11px; color: var(--slate); margin-top: 5px;">Consolidation pour le pilotage décisionnel.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flow-card">
            <span>Identity Hub</span>
            <strong>Directory & IAM</strong>
            <p style="font-size: 11px; color: var(--slate); margin-top: 5px;">Flux d'authentification et de sécurité.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-top: 25px; padding: 15px; background: rgba(10, 25, 47, 0.03); font-size: 12px; font-style: italic;">
          Note : La réduction de la complexité d'intégration est un levier majeur pour augmenter l'agilité des mises en production.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
